description:
<!--StartFragment-->

Miracles Everywhere is a Gospel Pop infused with an African-Caribbean Influence. It carries an Emblematic touch of the African Gospel Pop as can be felt in its amazing rhythmic blend of instrumentation and beats. Very Danceable and will most certainly get everyone on their feet, Maureen in her Lyrics wants everyone to look around and celebrate”Miracles Everywhere”. This song of Praise carries a message of Assurance and asserts our confidence and Faith in our Maker.
